    • TextButtonCell

      public TextButtonCell()
      Construct a TextButtonCell using the TextButtonCell.DefaultAppearance.

      The TextButtonCell.DefaultAppearance may be replaced with a more modern appearance in the future. If you want to stay up to date with the latest appearance, use this constructor. If you do not want the appearance to be updated with successive versions of GWT, create an TextButtonCell.Appearance and pass it to TextButtonCell(Appearance).
